high_descs: Walk towards the coffee maker on your left.
Pick up the spoon in front of the coffee maker.
Take a step to the right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the spoon in the gold cup.
Take the gold cup with the spoon out of the fridge and close it.
Turn left towards the white table on your right.
Place the cup in front of the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the cup with a spoon in front of the apple on the table.

high_descs: Go forward and then turn left at the coffee maker.
Take the spoon from the counter, in front of the coffee maker.
Go to the fridge, to the right of the coffee maker.
Put the spoon in the wine glass, in the fridge.
Pick up the wine glass from the fridge.
Turn left, then go straight, then turn right to face the table with the pan on it.
Put the wine glass on the right front corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a wine glass with a spoon in it on the table.

high_descs: Walk to the counter that's to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the spoon in front of the coffee maker.
Walk in front of the fridge.
Open the freezer door, put the spoon in a wine glass.
Take the wine glass with the spoon out of the freezer and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the white counter with the salt shaker.
Put the glass down on the right corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: To take a chilled glass out of the freezer.

high_descs: Walk straight and stop at the coffee maker on the left
Grab the spoon that is in front of the coffee maker
Turn right to the fridge
Open the fridge and put the spoon in the cup in the fridge
Grab the cup out of the fridge
Turn left and head to the white table
Place the cup on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a cup with a spoon in it on the white table

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter that is to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the spoon that is in front of the coffee maker.
With the spoon in hand go to the fridge.
Open the fridge. Place the spoon in the cup that is on the top shelf to the right of the tomato.
Pick up the cup on the top shelf with the spoon in it that is to the right of the tomato. Close the fridge.
With the cup with the spoon in it go to the table.
Place the cup with the spoon in it on the right front corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the cup with spoon on the table.
